OL,3,CNorth East has fewest number of
OL,4,Cdisability driving instructors in
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FNew figures released by the
OL,8,FAssociation of Disability Driving
OL,9,FInstructors show that the North East
OL,10,Fhas the joint fewest number of adapted
OL,11,Ftuition vehicles of any nation or
OL,12,Fregion in the UK.
OL,14,FTheir data suggests there are just 5
OL,15,Fdriving instructors in the region who
OL,16,Fhave these vehicles, compared with 20
OL,17,Fin the South East, 18 in the South
OL,18,FWest and 17 in the East Midlands.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
