OL,3,CNorth East has fewest number of
OL,4,Cdisability driving instructors in
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FAcross the country there are almost
OL,8,F40,000 Approved Driving Instructors,
OL,9,Fbut only 151 of them are able to teach
OL,10,Fdisabled people in adapted vehicles.
OL,12,FPaul Whitburn is one of the few
OL,13,Fdriving instructors who can teach
OL,14,Fdisabled learners and has told us
OL,15,Fwhile he finds the work fulfilling, he
OL,16,Frealises it is not for everyone.
