OL,3,CNorth East has fewest number of
OL,4,Cdisability driving instructors in
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FHe said, "You need a slightly larger
OL,8,Fvehicle, you need a series of
OL,9,Fadaptions, all this costs money, and
OL,10,Fby law you can't charge any more for
OL,11,Fthat.
OL,13,F"It reduces your profit margins, so
OL,14,Fpeople will say why should I invest in
OL,15,Fthat? But the work is very, very, very
OL,16,Frewarding, it's really enjoyable."
