OL,3,CNorth East has fewest number of
OL,4,Cdisability driving instructors in
OL,5,Ccountry
OL,7,FJohn Rogers, the founder of the
OL,8,FAssociation of Disability Driving
OL,9,FInstructors, is concerned that there
OL,10,Fis no motivation for driving
OL,11,Finstructors to adapt their vehicles.
OL,13,FHe said, "A lot of driving instructors
OL,14,Fare completely fully booked, so why
OL,15,Fwould they need to spend an extra
OL,16,F#1,000 to teach disabled people, when
OL,17,Fthey don't need to do that to keep
OL,18,Ftheir driving school afloat?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
